messages.message: Hey team / @mfichman. I'm looking for some early feedback on this PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/72681) for porting Cypress CI over to the ibdev-backend Crafting template. I got it working e2e, without actually rebuilding all services on every commit. The most challenging part we need to figure out is how to build all services reliably and quickly...
